00:33:08.420 --> 00:33:10.339
Come on. D.

493
00:33:10.422 --> 00:33:12.508
I'm out on parole. man.

494
00:33:12.591 --> 00:33:15.136
I can't go back to jail.
Please.

495
00:33:15.219 --> 00:33:16.553
I missed Hell's Kitchen.

496
00:33:16.637 --> 00:33:17.847
Yeah.

497
00:33:17.930 --> 00:33:20.224
It didn't miss you.

498
00:33:23.435 --> 00:33:24.436
Fine.

499
00:33:24.520 --> 00:33:26.773
Know what?
Be like that.

500
00:33:28.274 --> 00:33:31.027
'Cause we both know I'll be back out
by the end of the month...

501
00:33:35.656 --> 00:33:36.866
I'll see you then.

502
00:33:47.293 --> 00:33:48.836
Members only. pork chop.

503
00:33:48.920 --> 00:33:51.088
It's okay. I'm meeting a friend.

504
00:33:52.464 --> 00:33:53.966
Get lost or get hurt.

505
00:33:54.967 --> 00:33:58.637
He's a full-patch member
of the Dogs of Hell.

506
00:33:58.720 --> 00:34:00.347
I swear. I just need to talk to him.

507
00:34:00.431 --> 00:34:01.974
What's this big shot's name?

508
00:34:02.058 --> 00:34:03.392
Smitty.

509
00:34:05.477 --> 00:34:06.562
Don't move.

510
00:34:20.326 --> 00:34:21.618
Does it look like I'm packing?

511
00:34:21.702 --> 00:34:23.495
Gonna wish you were.

512
00:34:28.209 --> 00:34:29.710
Come with me.

513
00:34:54.026 --> 00:34:55.777
Look at this asshole.

514
00:35:06.205 --> 00:35:07.915
Says he's here to see Smitty.

515
00:35:11.710 --> 00:35:13.504
Old friend.

516
00:35:15.006 --> 00:35:16.673
- Old friend?
- Yeah.

517
00:35:16.757 --> 00:35:19.510
Third grade.
Sister Haney's class?

518
00:35:19.593 --> 00:35:21.470
She really had it in for us.

519
00:35:22.263 --> 00:35:25.099
Is he around or should I just...
Ow! No. no. no. no!

520
00:35:25.182 --> 00:35:27.018
Holy shit!

521
00:35:29.145 --> 00:35:32.273
- What's your name?
- Foggy! Franklin Nelson!

522
00:35:33.565 --> 00:35:34.566
Never heard of you.

523
00:35:34.650 --> 00:35:37.778
I've known Smitty
for a long time.

524
00:35:38.612 --> 00:35:40.114
Oh. yeah? Me. too.

525
00:35:40.197 --> 00:35:42.158
Obviously. we went on different
career paths along the way...

526
00:35:42.241 --> 00:35:44.076
- Is this funny to you?
- No.

527
00:35:44.160 --> 00:35:46.245
- No. sir.
- 'Cause I'm two seconds away

528
00:35:46.328 --> 00:35:48.998
- from slitting your throat.
- I'm not a cop. okay?

529
00:35:51.500 --> 00:35:52.709
You a fed?

530
00:35:52.793 --> 00:35:54.128
I'm a lawyer.

531
00:35:55.462 --> 00:35:58.215
Look. I just...
I just need five minutes

532
00:35:58.299 --> 00:36:01.385
with Smitty and then I swear. I'm gone.

533
00:36:01.468 --> 00:36:02.594
Yeah. you're gone now.

534
00:36:02.678 --> 00:36:06.307
Ever walk back in here again.
and you'll leave in pieces.

535
00:36:06.390 --> 00:36:08.267
Nod if you understand me.

536
00:36:13.605 --> 00:36:16.150
Take him out back.
show him how we feel about lawyers.

537
00:36:16.233 --> 00:36:17.359
No. please. no. no. no. no. no.

538
00:39:14.495 --> 00:39:16.622
It's okay.
I'm gonna get you down.

539
00:39:16.705 --> 00:39:19.750
I'm gonna get you down.
I'm gonna get you down.

540
00:39:27.716 --> 00:39:29.760
It was a mistake coming here.
I realize that.

541
00:39:29.843 --> 00:39:31.470
- Shut up!
- I just wanted to help people. I swear.

542
00:39:31.553 --> 00:39:33.930
- Smitty would understand!
- Smitty's dead. asshole.

543
00:39:34.014 --> 00:39:35.224
What?

544
00:39:36.892 --> 00:39:39.645
You have to believe me.
I... I didn't know that.

545
00:39:39.728 --> 00:39:41.021
Oh. I believe
there's a lot you don't know.

546
00:39:41.105 --> 00:39:42.314
Whoa. okay. look.

547
00:39:42.398 --> 00:39:45.234
Smitty was a long time ago.

548
00:39:45.317 --> 00:39:47.486
Couple years ago.
I helped a guy named Foster.

549
00:39:47.569 --> 00:39:49.238
- He was a biker!
- Not one of ours.

550
00:39:49.321 --> 00:39:50.781
- Ricky Wex?
- Shut up!

551
00:39:50.864 --> 00:39:52.324
I helped a guy named Pope!

552
00:39:53.409 --> 00:39:57.204
Yeah. the VA said that his injuries
weren't sustained during battle.

553
00:39:57.288 --> 00:39:58.914
but they were!

554
00:39:58.997 --> 00:40:01.792
They just didn't manifest themselves
for 20 years.

555
00:40:01.875 --> 00:40:04.795
Uh. we got his operation sorted and then.

556
00:40:04.878 --> 00:40:07.047
a couple of months later.
he was back on his Harley.

557
00:40:07.131 --> 00:40:10.217
doing whatever it is you guys do.
Which is none of my business!

558
00:40:11.552 --> 00:40:13.179
You helped Pope?

559
00:40:17.433 --> 00:40:18.600
Get the hell out of here.

560
00:40:20.477 --> 00:40:22.020
- Really?
- Now!

561
00:40:26.983 --> 00:40:28.402
What happened to Smitty?

562
00:40:31.197 --> 00:40:32.948
- You serious?
- I came here for a reason.

563
00:40:33.031 --> 00:40:34.450
I just need answers!

564
00:40:34.533 --> 00:40:38.119
Look. if I don't get answers.
a lot of innocent blood could be shed.

565
00:40:38.204 --> 00:40:41.623
People who both you and I care about
are gonna get hurt.

566
00:40:41.707 --> 00:40:43.875
And you don't seem like
the most sentimental guy.

567
00:40:43.959 --> 00:40:46.295
but you're still listening.

568
00:40:46.378 --> 00:40:51.508
And that knife isn't in my neck.
so I have to believe that right now...

569
00:40:52.759 --> 00:40:55.387
maybe you and I are on the same side.

570
00:40:56.972 --> 00:41:00.434
You got guts. Harvard.
I'll give you that.

571
00:41:01.852 --> 00:41:05.689
Columbia. actually. but it's not courage.

572
00:41:05.772 --> 00:41:07.483
It's more like sheer adrenaline.

573
00:41:09.109 --> 00:41:10.819
Hey. look. I wouldn't be asking.

574
00:41:10.902 --> 00:41:15.491
I wouldn't be here doing this
if it wasn't important.

575
00:41:26.543 --> 00:41:28.086
Smitty was on a run.

576
00:41:28.169 --> 00:41:31.298
I-90 with four brothers.
transporting a big score.

577
00:41:31.382 --> 00:41:35.594
They were hit by a goddamn army.
Their whole crew was cut to pieces.

578
00:41:35.677 --> 00:41:37.263
Left there like roadkill.

579
00:41:37.346 --> 00:41:39.473
- Any idea who did it?
- Nah.

580
00:41:39.556 --> 00:41:42.684
New crew. doesn't matter.
Whoever they are. we're gonna find 'em.

581
00:41:42.768 --> 00:41:46.104
And when we do. you wanna be
very far away from the action.

582
00:41:47.105 --> 00:41:50.108
You didn't hear none of this from me.
Now go.

583
00:41:51.818 --> 00:41:53.111
And don't come back.

584
00:42:06.500 --> 00:42:09.253
I always knew
the devil would come for me.

585
00:42:10.504 --> 00:42:12.506
But I thought I would be dead first.

586
00:42:12.589 --> 00:42:14.550
- I'm gonna get some help.
- No!

587
00:42:14.633 --> 00:42:17.052
No... no...

588
00:42:23.850 --> 00:42:25.394
Who did this?

589
00:42:26.186 --> 00:42:27.854
No one escapes this.

590
00:42:28.814 --> 00:42:31.900
No one can get away.

591
00:42:33.319 --> 00:42:34.736
Tell me.

592
00:42:42.494 --> 00:42:44.413
Tell me who they are.

593
00:42:48.709 --> 00:42:50.168
No "they."

594
00:42:50.251 --> 00:42:51.753
Him.

595
00:42:53.129 --> 00:42:54.673
It's one man.

596
00:43:21.992 --> 00:43:24.536
Hold it right there.

597
00:43:28.582 --> 00:43:31.292
Oh. my God!

598
00:43:32.836 --> 00:43:34.713
Oh. God.

599
00:43:34.796 --> 00:43:36.297
What was that?

600
00:43:36.382 --> 00:43:38.634
No. no. no. no. no. no. no.

601
00:43:38.717 --> 00:43:40.218
Shit.

602
00:43:40.301 --> 00:43:41.887
Someone's come to finish the job.

603
00:43:41.970 --> 00:43:43.639
Shh! Don't move.

604
00:43:44.556 --> 00:43:45.849
No. to hell with that.

605
00:43:52.272 --> 00:43:54.149
He's got a gun!

606
00:43:54.232 --> 00:43:56.735
Shit.

607
00:43:56.818 --> 00:43:59.029
Come on. come on. come on!

608
00:43:59.112 --> 00:44:00.822
Come on!

609
00:44:34.565 --> 00:44:37.233
Dear God.

610
00:44:37.317 --> 00:44:38.694
Shit.

611
00:44:38.777 --> 00:44:40.737
What? You...
You don't have the right keys?

612
00:44:40.821 --> 00:44:43.073
- Shut up! Shut up!
- Is this even your car?

613
00:44:43.156 --> 00:44:45.283
- Belonged to a friend.
- Where's he?

614
00:44:46.284 --> 00:44:47.619
He's dead.

615
00:44:48.829 --> 00:44:50.371
Get in!

616
00:46:46.822 --> 00:46:48.156
Bang.

617
00:46:48.998 --> 00:46:53.998
